Humanity is at the precipice. With a ravaged world below, man's only hope was to escape above the clouds. While providing momentary peace, their floating cities would eventually collapse, leaving just Empyrea.

Desperate to survive, most have traded freedom for security, except for Lucas Corvin. As tensions reach an all-time high, he discovers otherworldly forces working in the shadows not only those behind his plight, but a mystic power deep within him. Can he become the master of his fate and find salvation, or will his kind be harvested by those who conquered death? The odds are stacked against him, but he need not stand alone.

Judgment day approaches. Join those who fight for liberty. Rise in revolution!

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
